dmca.title: NeoPets sends Pink Poogles a furball
dmca.body:
Dear Owner/Webmaster of http://www.pinkpoogletoy.com:
		
	NeoPets.com, which has millions of registered users, is a COPPA
(Children's Online Privacy Protection Act)-compliant interactive
entertainment website targeted primarily to children and young people
ranging in age from 6 to 20 years old. 	

	We are contacting you regarding your web site
http://www.pinkpoogletoy.com.  As you should be aware, since at least
